          My name is Adam Christopher Backlas Widjaja. Take the initials of my
          name, and you got ACBW. Welcome to my site!
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="post-block">
        <%= image_tag "https://s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/wpacbw/uploads/2016/12/s_IMG_20161106_143857.jpg", alt: "Tokyo Cycling Diary", class: "post-block-image" %>
